title: Galion teachers set to tour Galion businesses Oct. 23 (Galion City School District)
text: ( Source : Galion City School District ) The education and manufacturing communities in Crawford County are coming together to raise awareness for, and get students interested in, careers in manufacturing. The program is called WAGE , Workforce
